IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. RATINGENGINE.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 BASE-PREMIUM PIC 9(5)V99 VALUE 100.00.
01 FACTOR PIC 9(3)V99 VALUE 1.20.
01 FINAL-PREMIUM PIC 9(6)V99.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY "RATING ENGINE START".

    COMPUTE FINAL-PREMIUM = BASE-PREMIUM * FACTOR.

    DISPLAY "BASE PREMIUM: " BASE-PREMIUM.
    DISPLAY "FACTOR: " FACTOR.
    DISPLAY "FINAL PREMIUM: " FINAL-PREMIUM.

    DISPLAY "BUILD SUCCESSFUL".
    GOBACK.